        "faq_accordion": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "name": "FAQ Accordion",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "plus",
            "dividers": true,
            "type_preset": "h6",
            "inherit_color_scheme": true,
            "color_scheme": "",
            "border": "none",
            "border_width": 1,
            "border_opacity": 100,
            "border_radius": 0,
            "padding-block-start": 0,
            "padding-block-end": 0,
            "padding-inline-start": 0,
            "padding-inline-end": 0
          },
          "blocks": {
            "faq_1": {
              "type": "_accordion-row",
              "name": "FAQ 1",
              "settings": {
                "heading": "What fabrics do you use?",
                "open_by_default": false,
                "icon": "none"
              },
              "blocks": {
                "faq_1_text": {
                  "type": "text",
                  "settings": {
                    "text": "<p>We use a range of proprietary fabric blends — CloudSoft™, LuxeModal™, AirSoft™, EcoSoft™, and more — each engineered for softness, breathability, and all-day comfort. Visit our Fabrics page to learn more about each one.</p>",
                    "type_preset": "paragraph",
                    "font": "var(--font-body--family)",
                    "font_size": "0.9375rem",
                    "line_height": "1.7",
                    "alignment": "left",
                    "color": "var(--color-foreground)"
                  }
                }
              },
              "block_order": ["faq_1_text"]
            },
            "faq_2": {
              "type": "_accordion-row",
              "name": "FAQ 2",
              "settings": {
                "heading": "How do I find my size?",
                "open_by_default": false,
                "icon": "none"
              },
              "blocks": {
                "faq_2_text": {
                  "type": "text",
                  "settings": {
                    "text": "<p>Each product page includes a size guide with detailed measurements. Our pieces are generally true to size — if you're between sizes, we recommend sizing up for a relaxed fit or sizing down for a fitted look.</p>",
                    "type_preset": "paragraph",
                    "font": "var(--font-body--family)",
                    "font_size": "0.9375rem",
                    "line_height": "1.7",
                    "alignment": "left",
                    "color": "var(--color-foreground)"
                  }
                }
              },
              "block_order": ["faq_2_text"]
            },
            "faq_3": {
              "type": "_accordion-row",
              "name": "FAQ 3",
              "settings": {
                "heading": "What is your return policy?",
                "open_by_default": false,
                "icon": "none"
              },
              "blocks": {
                "faq_3_text": {
                  "type": "text",
                  "settings": {
                    "text": "<p>We accept returns within 14 days of delivery. Items must be unworn, unwashed, and in original packaging. Sale items are final sale. To initiate a return, contact us at hello@secondform.in.</p>",
                    "type_preset": "paragraph",
                    "font": "var(--font-body--family)",
                    "font_size": "0.9375rem",
                    "line_height": "1.7",
                    "alignment": "left",
                    "color": "var(--color-foreground)"
                  }
                }
              },
              "block_order": ["faq_3_text"]
            },
            "faq_4": {
              "type": "_accordion-row",
              "name": "FAQ 4",
              "settings": {
                "heading": "Do you offer free shipping?",
                "open_by_default": false,
                "icon": "none"
              },
              "blocks": {
                "faq_4_text": {
                  "type": "text",
                  "settings": {
                    "text": "<p>Yes — we offer free shipping on all orders above ₹2,499. Standard delivery takes 3–5 business days. Express options are available at checkout.</p>",
                    "type_preset": "paragraph",
                    "font": "var(--font-body--family)",
                    "font_size": "0.9375rem",
                    "line_height": "1.7",
                    "alignment": "left",
                    "color": "var(--color-foreground)"
                  }
                }
              },
              "block_order": ["faq_4_text"]
            },
            "faq_5": {
              "type": "_accordion-row",
              "name": "FAQ 5",
              "settings": {
                "heading": "Are your products sustainable?",
                "open_by_default": false,
                "icon": "none"
              },
              "blocks": {
                "faq_5_text": {
                  "type": "text",
                  "settings": {
                    "text": "<p>Sustainability is a core part of what we do. Our EcoSoft™ and EcoLite™ fabrics are made from recycled materials. We're continuously working to reduce our environmental footprint across packaging, production, and supply chain.</p>",
                    "type_preset": "paragraph",
                    "font": "var(--font-body--family)",
                    "font_size": "0.9375rem",
                    "line_height": "1.7",
                    "alignment": "left",
                    "color": "var(--color-foreground)"
                  }
                }
              },
              "block_order": ["faq_5_text"]
            },
            "faq_6": {
              "type": "_accordion-row",
              "name": "FAQ 6",
              "settings": {
                "heading": "How do I care for my Second Form pieces?",
                "open_by_default": false,
                "icon": "none"
              },
              "blocks": {
                "faq_6_text": {
                  "type": "text",
                  "settings": {
                    "text": "<p>Machine wash cold on a gentle cycle. Do not bleach. Tumble dry low or lay flat to dry. Avoid ironing directly on prints. Following these steps will keep your pieces looking and feeling their best.</p>",
                    "type_preset": "paragraph",
                    "font": "var(--font-body--family)",
                    "font_size": "0.9375rem",
                    "line_height": "1.7",
                    "alignment": "left",
                    "color": "var(--color-foreground)"
                  }
                }
              },
              "block_order": ["faq_6_text"]
            }
          },
          "block_order": ["faq_1", "faq_2", "faq_3", "faq_4", "faq_5", "faq_6"]
        }
      },
